===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 19 people, 9 households, and 5 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A25005&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A25005&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 76.4 inhabitants per square mile (29.5/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 13 housing units at an average density of 52.3 per square mile (20.2/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A25005&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref>

Of households, 22.2% had children under the age of 18 living in them. Of all households, 33.3% were married-couple households, 0.0% were cohabitating couples, 0.0% were households with a male householder and no spouse or partner present, and 66.7% were households with a female householder and no spouse or partner present. About 44.4% of households were non-families, 44.4% of all households were made up of individuals, and 22.2% had someone living alone who was 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age was 61.5 years. 0.0% of residents were under the age of 18, 5.3% were under the age of 20, 0.0% were between the ages of 20 and 24, 15.8% were from 25 to 44, 42.1% were from 45 to 64, and 36.8% were 65 years of age or older. For every 100 females there were 72.7 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 72.7 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/><ref name="Census2020PL"/>

Of housing units, 30.8% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

